      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I GOT CHILLS NZ (12) is a newcomer to the Jason Grimson yard from Queensland where he had been producing some consistent form before breaking last start. Draws out but is proven at this distance and could make an immediate impact. MAJOR REASON (8) made it two wins in four outings since joining Seaton Grima when he led and kept going to score by close to 3m at Newcastle last week. Draws wider but this looks a suitable assignment. IM ROCKIN IT (3) missed the placings after working last time but he was good when he came from this barrier to miss narrowly at this circuit and distance prior. Should be close to peak fitness now. LOVE A BELLE (5) came from this barrier to win at this circuit and distance two back before she was beaten only 2.6m in a handy line-up of mares last week. Go well.",
